The Raviz Ashtamudi is indeed a treat for Architecture lovers. The Nalukettu architecture of Kerala is very unique. It draws heavily from the Dravidian and Vedic styles of construction. At The Raviz Ashtamudi, we take utmost care at preserving and showcasing the traditional architectural marvels of our land.
